dc_title_s: Insurance maps of Minneapolis, Minnesota, last revised 1929, Volume 2
dc_description_s: Updated with pasteover slips and additional sheets. Date of last revision varies between 1924-1930. Each volume includes a map of ward lines and district lines and a volume boundary map (index map to all volumes). Volumes 2 and 3 include map of congested district, 200 feet to 1 inch.|v.2: sheets 111-223|70 Centimeters|Scale 1:600. 50 feet to 1 inch|City of Minneapolis Archives
